Eva Longoria, 47, wowed her 8.7 million Instagram followers with a jaw-dropping snap of herself lounging in the sun. The Desperate Housewives star held the camera high so fans could get a full view of her sculpted body in a skimpy red bikini.Eva looked stunning as she pouted for the camera, shielding her eyes from the sun with some dark sunglasses.A few hours later, she shared a cheeky transformation video of herself getting ready for a night out.  The clip began with Eva posing on some stairs looking very glamorous in a purple, leather suit.It then cut to a makeup-free Eva in her kitchen. She was wearing a dressing gown with her hair thrown on top of her head as she made some coffee.The voiceover said: “I love a girl that can slay one day and look homeless the next. Balance baby!”